@page "/disclaimer"
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization
@attribute [AllowAnonymous]

<PageTitle>Disclaimer & Policies - Castle of Happiness</PageTitle>

<div class="container mt-4 mb-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4">Disclaimer & Policies</h1>

    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">General Betting Rules</h4>
            <p class="card-text">
                Castle of Happiness is powered by Kambi. All wagers are settled in accordance with the Kambi Sportsbook General Betting Rules.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">Odds Adjustment Policy</h4>
            <p class="card-text">
                To ensure we provide the fastest possible service and maintain access to the best market rates, Castle of Happiness rounds all odds down to the nearest 0.05 increment. This prevents delays caused by minor, real-time market fluctuations.
            </p>
            <div class="alert alert-info mt-3 mb-0" role="alert">
                <strong>Example:</strong> Odds of 2.57 will be processed as 2.55.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">Free Bet Policy</h4>
            <p class="card-text">
                Free Bets are awarded as "Net Free Bets". This means that when a wager is placed using a Free Bet, only the net winnings (total return minus the original Free Bet stake) will be credited to your account balance if the bet wins. The original Free Bet stake is not returned.
            </p>
            <div class="alert alert-info mt-3 mb-0" role="alert">
                <strong>Example:</strong> A 500kr Free Bet placed at odds of 3.00 would return 1000kr in net winnings (1500kr total return - 500kr stake).
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">Referral Program Rules</h4>
            <p class="card-text">
                We reward players who bring active, genuine friends to our platform. To protect against bonus abuse, Free Bets (FB) earned through referrals are subject to the following validation conditions before they can be fully credited or cashed out:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Turnover Requirements (Tiered Payout):</strong> The Free Bet reward is released in stages based on the referred user's total betting turnover:
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>20%</strong> of the Free Bet is paid out when the new user reaches <strong>5,000 kr</strong> in turnover.</li>
                        <li>An additional <strong>30%</strong> is paid out when the new user reaches <strong>15,000 kr</strong> in total turnover.</li>
                        <li>The final <strong>50%</strong> is paid out when the new user reaches <strong>30,000 kr</strong> in total turnover.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><strong>Minimum Odds:</strong> Only settled bets placed with odds of <strong>1.50 or higher</strong> count towards this turnover.</li>
            </ul>
            <h5 class="mt-4 mb-2 fw-bold">Welcome Bonus for Referred Users</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
                New users who join through a referral link are eligible for a welcome bonus in the form of a Net Free Bet. To unlock this welcome bonus, the new user must first place settled bets totaling the welcome bonus amount on markets with minimum odds of <strong>1.50</strong>.
            </p>
            <div class="alert alert-secondary mt-3 mb-0" role="alert">
                <i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i> Castle of Happiness reserves the right to withhold referral bonuses or cancel pending Free Bets if we detect coordinated betting, matched betting, or fake accounts designed solely to exploit the referral program.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">Settlement Days</h4>
            <p class="card-text">
                On settlement days, you must settle your account based on your current Balance, even if you have unsettled bets. We run our settlement process just after 23:59 on Sunday evenings. Whatever your Balance is at that time determines what you owe. Even if you have a bet that settles on Monday, you must pay your full negative Balance as it stood on Sunday at 23:59.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">Withdrawal Policy</h4>
            <p class="card-text">
                To receive your payout on Monday, your withdrawal request must be submitted before kl. 23:59 on Sunday. Any requests placed after 23:59 on Sunday will not be paid out on Monday, and you will have to wait until the settlement on the following Monday.
            </p>
            <p class="card-text mt-3">
                <strong>Free Bet Turnover Requirement:</strong><br />
                New customers who receive a Free Bet must meet a turnover requirement before any funds can be withdrawn. The required turnover is <strong>3x the Free Bet amount</strong>, and only settled bets with odds of <strong>1.50 or higher</strong> count towards this requirement.
                <br />
                <span class="text-muted small"><em>(Example: If you receive a 2,500 kr Free Bet, you must place eligible bets totaling 7,500 kr before initiating a withdrawal.)</em></span>
            </p>
            <div class="alert alert-warning mt-3 mb-0" role="alert">
                <strong>Important:</strong> Early withdrawals or withdrawals requested outside of the standard payment day are subject to a 25% fee.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>